<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. قَدْ حَارَ فِيهِ فِكْرَةُ الإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَجَمَالُهَا قِشْرٌ رَقِيقٌ تَحْتَهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَا شِئْتَ مِنْ عَيْبٍ وَمِنْ نُقْصَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نَقْدٌ رَدِيءٌ فَوْقَهُ مِنْ فِضَّةٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>شَيْءٌ يُظَنُّ بِهِ مِنْ الأَثْمَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَالنَّاقِدُونَ يَرَوْنَ مَاذَا تَحْتَهُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَالنَّاسُ أَكْثَرْهُم مِن الْعُمْيَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أَمَّا جَمِيلاتُ الْوُجُوهِ فَخَائِنَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تُ بُعُولَهنَّ وَهُنَّ لِلأَخْدَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَالْحَافِظَاتُ الْغَيْبِ مِنْهُنَّ الَّتِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>قَدْ أَصْبَحَتْ فَرْدًا مِنْ النّسْوَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَانْظُرْ مَصَارِعَ مَنْ يَلِيكَ وَمَنْ خَلا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مِنْ قَبْلُ مِن شَيْبٍ وَمِنْ شُبَّانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَارْغَبْ بِعَقْلِكَ أَنْ تَبِيعَ الْغَالِي الْـ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>بَاقِي بِذَا الأَدْنَى الَّذِي هُوَ فَانِي<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>إِنْ كَانَ قَدْ أَعْيَاكَ خُودٌ مِثْلَ مَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>تَبْغِي وَلَمْ تَظْفَرْ إِلَى ذَا الآنِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَاخْطُبْ مِنَ الرَّحْمَنِ خُودًا ثُمَّ قَدِّ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مْ مَهْرَهَا مَا دُمْتَ ذَا إِمْكَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>ذَاكَ النِّكَاحُ عَلَيْكَ أَيْسَرُ إِنْ يَكُنْ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>